1
00:00:07,709 --> 00:00:10,083
Katara: WATER...

2
00:00:10,125 --> 00:00:11,709
EARTH...

3
00:00:11,750 --> 00:00:13,834
FIRE...

4
00:00:13,875 --> 00:00:16,291
AIR.

5
00:00:16,333 --> 00:00:20,291
LONG AGO, THE FOUR NATIONS
LIVED TOGETHER IN HARMONY.

6
00:00:20,333 --> 00:00:24,792
THEN EVERYTHING CHANGED
WHEN THE FIRE NATION ATTACKED.

7
00:00:24,834 --> 00:00:28,667
ONLY THE AVATAR,
MASTER OF ALL FOUR ELEMENTS,
COULD STOP THEM.

8
00:00:28,709 --> 00:00:32,250
BUT WHEN THE WORLD
NEEDED HIM MOST, HE VANISHED.

9
00:00:32,291 --> 00:00:36,417
100 YEARS PASSED
AND MY BROTHER AND I DISCOVERED
THE NEW AVATAR...

10
00:00:36,458 --> 00:00:38,375
AN AIRBENDER NAMED AANG.

11
00:00:38,417 --> 00:00:40,375
AND ALTHOUGH HIS AIRBENDING
SKILLS ARE GREAT

12
00:00:40,417 --> 00:00:43,834
HE HAS A LOT TO LEARN BEFORE
HE'S READY TO SAVE ANYONE.

13
00:00:43,875 --> 00:00:47,250
BUT I BELIEVE AANG
CAN SAVE THE WORLD.

14
00:00:47,291 --> 00:00:49,375
♪

15
00:00:55,875 --> 00:00:59,291
Ozai: YOU HAVE REDEEMED
YOURSELF, MY SON.

16
00:00:59,333 --> 00:01:01,041
WELCOME HOME.

17
00:01:01,083 --> 00:01:03,375
I KNOW ONE THING I CARE ABOUT.

18
00:01:03,417 --> 00:01:06,792
I CARE ABOUT YOU.

19
00:01:06,834 --> 00:01:08,917
Sokka: A SOLAR ECLIPSE
IS COMING.

20
00:01:08,959 --> 00:01:11,458
THE SUN WILL BE ENTIRELY
BLOCKED OUT BY THE MOON

21
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:13,875
AND THE FIREBENDERS
WILL BE HELPLESS.

22
00:01:13,917 --> 00:01:16,542
THAT'S THE DAY WE NEED TO INVADE
THE FIRE NATION.

23
00:01:16,583 --> 00:01:18,625
THE DAY OF BLACK SUN.

24
00:01:18,667 --> 00:01:21,375
I'VE ALWAYS KNOWN THAT I WOULD
HAVE TO FACE THE FIRE LORD.

25
00:01:21,417 --> 00:01:24,500
BUT NOW I KNOW
I NEED TO DO IT ALONE.

26
00:01:24,542 --> 00:01:27,792
♪

27
00:01:35,834 --> 00:01:38,291
[APPA GROANS]

28
00:01:38,333 --> 00:01:40,083
[MOMO CHATTERS]

29
00:01:40,125 --> 00:01:43,083
THIS IS IT, THE OFFICIAL
RENDEZVOUS POINT
FOR THE INVASION FORCE.

30
00:01:43,125 --> 00:01:45,500
Toph: HOW DID YOU PICK
THIS PLACE?

31
00:01:45,542 --> 00:01:48,792
Sokka: BEFORE WE SPLIT UP,
MY DAD AND I FOUND THIS ISLAND
ON A MAP.

32
00:01:48,834 --> 00:01:52,125
IT'S UNINHABITED, AND THE HARBOR
SURROUNDED BY CLIFFS SEEMED LIKE
THE PERFECT SECLUDED PLACE.

33
00:01:52,166 --> 00:01:53,750
Katara: NICE CHOICE, SOKKA.

34
00:01:53,792 --> 00:01:55,792
AND WE'RE HERE FOUR DAYS
AHEAD OF SCHEDULE.

35
00:01:55,834 --> 00:01:58,041
WAIT, FOUR DAYS?

36
00:01:58,083 --> 00:02:00,834
THE INVASION'S IN FOUR DAYS?

37
00:02:00,875 --> 00:02:02,625
[YAWNS]

38
00:02:02,667 --> 00:02:05,375
WHATEVER, THAT'S, LIKE,
FOUR DAYS FROM NOW.

39
00:02:05,417 --> 00:02:07,375
LET'S JUST CALM DOWN AND...

40
00:02:07,417 --> 00:02:09,583
[SNORING...]

41
00:02:09,625 --> 00:02:11,375
SOKKA'S GOT THE RIGHT
IDEA, AANG.

42
00:02:11,417 --> 00:02:13,333
WE'RE HERE, WE'RE READY.

43
00:02:13,375 --> 00:02:16,875
THE BEST THING WE CAN DO NOW
IS GET PLENTY OF REST.

44
00:02:16,917 --> 00:02:18,750
[GROANS] I GUESS.

45
00:02:37,917 --> 00:02:40,625
Aang: YOUR DAYS OF TYRANNY
ARE OVER, FIRE LORD.

46
00:02:40,667 --> 00:02:43,417
I'M BRINGING YOU DOWN.

47
00:02:43,458 --> 00:02:45,458
REALLY?

48
00:02:45,500 --> 00:02:48,083
HOW DO YOU PLAN ON DOING THAT

49
00:02:48,125 --> 00:02:50,917
WHEN YOU'RE NOT EVEN
WEARING PANTS?

50
00:02:50,959 --> 00:02:52,375
[YELLS]

51
00:02:52,417 --> 00:02:54,250
OH, NO.

52
00:03:01,667 --> 00:03:04,542
[CACKLING...]

53
00:03:09,875 --> 00:03:11,750
[GASPS]

54
00:03:11,792 --> 00:03:13,834
[GRUNTING]

55
00:03:13,875 --> 00:03:15,125
[SIGHS]

56
00:03:15,166 --> 00:03:16,500
[MOMO CHATTERS]

57
00:03:16,542 --> 00:03:18,208
IT WAS JUST A DREAM, MOMO.

58
00:03:18,250 --> 00:03:20,083
I STILL HAVE MY PANTS.

59
00:03:20,125 --> 00:03:21,750
[CHATTERING]

60
00:03:21,792 --> 00:03:24,917
WELL, I BETTER KEEP TRAINING.

61
00:03:31,208 --> 00:03:32,500
[CHATTERS]

62
00:03:39,875 --> 00:03:42,458
FRESH FRUIT, PRINCE ZUKO?

63
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:44,834
MAY I WASH YOUR FEET, SIR?

64
00:03:44,875 --> 00:03:47,667
HEAD MASSAGE?

65
00:03:47,709 --> 00:03:49,792
HOT TOWEL?

66
00:03:59,959 --> 00:04:02,291
[CROWD CHEERING...]

67
00:04:02,333 --> 00:04:06,792
[GIRLS LAUGHING...]

68
00:04:06,834 --> 00:04:09,125
[LAUGHING]

69
00:04:09,166 --> 00:04:10,583
OH...

70
00:04:10,625 --> 00:04:12,750
PRINCE ZUKO, IS SOMETHING WRONG?

71
00:04:12,792 --> 00:04:14,667
YOU DIDN'T TAKE THE PALANQUIN.

72
00:04:14,709 --> 00:04:17,000
I'M JUST GOING TO MAI'S HOUSE,
IT'S NOT FAR.

73
00:04:17,041 --> 00:04:19,959
IT'S NOT A PRINCE'S PLACE
TO WALK ANYWHERE, SIR.

74
00:04:39,166 --> 00:04:41,917
[THUDDING...]

75
00:04:55,542 --> 00:04:58,250
HEY, HOW LONG HAVE YOU BEEN UP?

76
00:04:58,291 --> 00:05:00,291
A COUPLE HOURS.

77
00:05:00,333 --> 00:05:03,709
I GOT A LOT MORE SKILLS TO
REFINE IF I'M GONNA FIGHT OZAI.

78
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:07,000
Katara: YOU KNOW, THERE IS
SUCH A THING AS OVERTRAINING.

79
00:05:07,041 --> 00:05:09,625
[GRUNTING]

80
00:05:16,208 --> 00:05:18,583
YOU DON'T GET IT, DO YOU?

81
00:05:18,625 --> 00:05:22,250
MY FORM IS BAD, I'M SLOPPY,
AND I STILL DON'T KNOW
ANY FIREBENDING.

82
00:05:22,291 --> 00:05:25,709
NOT EVEN THE BASICS.

83
00:05:25,750 --> 00:05:28,709
THAT'S OK, AANG,
THE ECLIPSE WILL BLOCK
ALL FIREBENDING ANYWAY.

84
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:30,083
YOU DON'T NEED TO KNOW ANY.

85
00:05:30,125 --> 00:05:31,875
PLUS, IT'S A STUPID ELEMENT.

86
00:05:31,917 --> 00:05:34,750
OK, WELL, I STILL HAVE TO
WORK ON EVERYTHING ELSE.

87
00:05:34,792 --> 00:05:37,291
I BETTER SPEND
THE WHOLE DAY TRAINING.

88
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:57,667
[YAWNS]

89
00:05:57,709 --> 00:05:58,917
GOOD NIGHT, KATARA.

90
00:05:58,959 --> 00:06:00,458
GOOD NIGHT, SOKKA.

91
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:02,458
GOOD NIGHT, TOPH.

92
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:04,750
GOOD NIGHT, APPA,
GOOD NIGHT, MOMO.

93
00:06:04,792 --> 00:06:06,083
GOOD NIGHT, APPA AND MO...

94
00:06:06,125 --> 00:06:07,709
GO TO SLEEP, ALREADY.

95
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:22,000
[SNAPS FINGERS]

96
00:06:26,750 --> 00:06:28,917
YOUR DAYS OF TYRANNY
ARE OVER, FIRE LORD.

97
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:31,125
I'M BRINGING YOU DOWN.

98
00:06:31,166 --> 00:06:34,917
AND THIS TIME I BROUGHT PANTS.

99
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:36,917
SO IT SEEMS.

100
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:41,333
BUT ARE YOU PREPARED
FOR YOUR MATHEMATICS TEST?

101
00:06:41,375 --> 00:06:43,166
MATH TEST?

102
00:06:43,208 --> 00:06:46,250
OH, NO, I FORGOT ALL ABOUT
THE MATH TEST.

103
00:06:46,291 --> 00:06:47,875
[OZAI CACKLING]

104
00:06:47,917 --> 00:06:51,417
[AANG SCREAMS]

105
00:06:51,458 --> 00:06:52,834
[GASPING]

106
00:06:52,875 --> 00:06:54,834
I'VE GOT TO BE READY.

107
00:07:03,750 --> 00:07:06,041
AANG, IT'S THE MIDDLE
OF THE NIGHT.

108
00:07:06,083 --> 00:07:08,333
YOU NEED TO GO BACK TO SLEEP.

109
00:07:08,375 --> 00:07:11,166
BUT I FORGOT MY PANTS
AND MY MATH TEST.

110
00:07:11,208 --> 00:07:12,625
[SIGHS]

111
00:07:16,375 --> 00:07:18,041
AANG, SLEEP.

112
00:07:18,083 --> 00:07:20,542
PLEASE, FOR ME.

113
00:07:30,208 --> 00:07:32,750
[SHEEP BAAS]

114
00:07:32,792 --> 00:07:35,041
TELL ME, IF YOU COULD HAVE
ANYTHING YOU WANTED RIGHT NOW

115
00:07:35,083 --> 00:07:37,000
WHAT WOULD IT BE?

116
00:07:37,041 --> 00:07:41,500
HMM... A BIG FANCY FRUIT TART
WITH ROSE PETALS ON TOP.

117
00:07:41,542 --> 00:07:45,458
YOU KNOW, BEING A PRINCE
AND ALL, I MIGHT JUST
BE ABLE TO MAKE THAT HAPPEN.

118
00:07:45,500 --> 00:07:48,375
[LAUGHS] THAT WOULD
BE IMPRESSIVE.

119
00:07:48,417 --> 00:07:51,917
DO YOU THINK YOU CAN FIND
A FRESH FRUIT TART FOR THE LADY?

120
00:07:51,959 --> 00:07:53,375
WITH ROSE PETALS ON TOP?

121
00:07:53,417 --> 00:07:55,250
EXCELLENT CHOICE, SIR.

122
00:07:55,291 --> 00:07:58,792
I GUESS THERE ARE SOME
NICE PERKS THAT COME WITH
BEING ROYALTY.

123
00:07:58,834 --> 00:08:00,959
THOUGH THERE'S
ANNOYING STUFF TOO.

124
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:03,792
LIKE THAT ALL-DAY WAR MEETING
COMING UP.

125
00:08:03,834 --> 00:08:06,083
WAR MEETING,
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

126
00:08:06,125 --> 00:08:07,542
AZULA MENTIONED SOMETHING.

127
00:08:07,583 --> 00:08:09,792
I, I ASSUMED YOU WERE GOING TOO.

128
00:08:09,834 --> 00:08:12,917
I GUESS I WASN'T INVITED.

129
00:08:15,792 --> 00:08:18,542
Ozai: WAKE UP, AANG.

130
00:08:18,583 --> 00:08:21,333
WAKE UP, SLEEPYHEAD.

131
00:08:21,375 --> 00:08:23,417
RISE AND SHINE.

132
00:08:23,458 --> 00:08:25,166
YOU OVERSLEPT.

133
00:08:25,208 --> 00:08:26,875
YOU MISSED THE INVASION.

134
00:08:26,917 --> 00:08:29,709
[CACKLING...]

135
00:08:34,834 --> 00:08:37,875
SOKKA, GET UP, I NEED TO KNOW
WHAT DAY IT IS.

136
00:08:37,917 --> 00:08:39,959
WHAT, WHO'S TALKING?

137
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:42,500
OW.

138
00:08:42,542 --> 00:08:46,917
RELAX, IT'S STILL TWO DAYS
BEFORE THE INVASION.

139
00:08:46,959 --> 00:08:49,625
SOKKA, YOU'VE GOT TO GET UP
AND DRILL YOUR
ROCK-CLIMBING EXERCISES.

140
00:08:49,667 --> 00:08:51,667
WHAT?

141
00:08:51,709 --> 00:08:54,250
IN ONE OF MY DREAMS,
YOU WERE RUNNING FROM
FIRE NATION SOLDIERS

142
00:08:54,291 --> 00:08:55,875
TRYING TO CLIMB THIS CLIFF

143
00:08:55,917 --> 00:08:57,750
BUT YOU WERE TOO SLOW
AND THEY GOT YOU.

144
00:08:57,792 --> 00:09:00,709
BUT THAT WAS JUST A DREAM,
I'M A GREAT CLIMBER.

145
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:03,959
THEN CLIMB THAT CLIFF,
CLIMB IT FAST.

146
00:09:11,625 --> 00:09:15,250
STUPID AVATAR, STUPID CLIFF,
STUPID DREAM.

147
00:09:15,291 --> 00:09:18,709
I CAN CLIMB FAST.

148
00:09:18,750 --> 00:09:21,041
DON'T DRINK THAT!
[SOKKA SCREAMS]

149
00:09:21,083 --> 00:09:23,500
WHY, IS IT POISONED?

150
00:09:23,542 --> 00:09:25,917
IN MY DREAM, WE WERE RIGHT
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE INVASION

151
00:09:25,959 --> 00:09:28,417
AND YOU HAD TO STOP
TO USE THE BATHROOM.

152
00:09:28,458 --> 00:09:30,458
WE DIED BECAUSE OF YOUR
TINY BLADDER.

153
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:32,709
AND YOU NEED TO START
WEARING YOUR HAIR UP.

154
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:35,542
IN MY DREAM, YOUR HAIR
GOT CAUGHT IN A TRAIN AND...

155
00:09:35,583 --> 00:09:37,333
AANG, I KNOW YOU'RE JUST
TRYING TO HELP.

156
00:09:37,375 --> 00:09:39,125
BUT YOU REALLY NEED TO
GET A GRIP.

157
00:09:39,166 --> 00:09:40,542
YOU'RE UNRAVELING.

158
00:09:40,583 --> 00:09:42,834
[SIGHS]

159
00:09:42,875 --> 00:09:47,709
YOU'RE RIGHT,
I'M LOSING MY MIND.

160
00:09:47,750 --> 00:09:49,250
[SCREAMS]

161
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,166
IT'S LIKE EVERY TIME
I THINK ABOUT HOW STRESSED I AM

162
00:09:56,208 --> 00:09:58,083
I JUST END UP MORE STRESSED.

163
00:09:58,125 --> 00:10:00,333
I'M LIKE A BIG GROWING SNOWBALL
OF NERVES.

164
00:10:00,375 --> 00:10:02,709
OF COURSE YOU ARE.

165
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:05,333
THAT'S 'CAUSE YOU GOTTA FIGHT
THE FIRE LORD, THE BADDEST MAN
ON THE PLANET.

166
00:10:05,375 --> 00:10:07,750
AND YOU BETTER WIN,
OR WE'RE ALL DONE FOR.

167
00:10:07,792 --> 00:10:09,333
SOKKA, YOU'RE NOT HELPING.

168
00:10:09,375 --> 00:10:11,000
WHAT?

169
00:10:11,041 --> 00:10:14,291
IT'S TRUE, THAT'S THE DEAL,
HE KNOWS IT.

170
00:10:14,333 --> 00:10:16,583
[WHIMPERING]

171
00:10:16,625 --> 00:10:18,834
YOU KNOW WHAT,
I'VE GOT JUST THE THING.

172
00:10:18,875 --> 00:10:21,750
GET READY TO BE DE-STRESSIFIED.

173
00:10:25,208 --> 00:10:28,875
...THESE YOGA STRETCHES
CAN REALLY WORK WONDERS
IF YOU DO THEM IN EXTREME HEAT.

174
00:10:28,917 --> 00:10:31,250
REACH UP.

175
00:10:31,291 --> 00:10:33,458
REACH FOR THE SUN.

176
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:37,834
FEEL YOUR CHI PATHS CLEARING.

177
00:10:37,875 --> 00:10:39,875
NOW CLOSE YOUR EYES.

178
00:10:39,917 --> 00:10:41,667
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

179
00:10:41,709 --> 00:10:43,750
I FEEL...

180
00:10:43,792 --> 00:10:45,291
REALLY WARM.

181
00:10:45,333 --> 00:10:47,333
Katara: GOOD, GOOD.

182
00:10:47,375 --> 00:10:49,083
GO ON.

183
00:10:49,125 --> 00:10:51,834
LIKE THERE'S THIS WARM FEELING
ALL AROUND ME.

184
00:10:51,875 --> 00:10:54,542
THIS HEAT.

185
00:10:54,583 --> 00:10:58,834
LIKE I'M IN THE FIRE LORD'S
PALACE AND HE'S SHOOTING
A BUNCH OF FIREBALLS AT ME.

186
00:10:58,875 --> 00:11:02,750
AND THE WHOLE WORLD IS BEING
ENGULFED IN FLAMES.

187
00:11:02,792 --> 00:11:06,083
MAYBE YOUR STRESS IS THE KIND
YOU NEED TO TALK OUT.

188
00:11:06,125 --> 00:11:09,917
[PANTING]

189
00:11:09,959 --> 00:11:14,250
WHY DON'T YOU GET RIGHT DOWN
TO BUSINESS AND TELL ME
WHAT'S BEEN BOTHERING YOU?

190
00:11:14,291 --> 00:11:16,083
YOU KNOW WHAT'S BOTHERING ME.

191
00:11:16,125 --> 00:11:18,792
I HAVE TO FIGHT THE FIRE LORD
IN A FEW DAYS.

192
00:11:18,834 --> 00:11:22,959
MM-HMM... TELL ME MORE
ABOUT THIS... FIRE LORD.

193
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,625
WHY ARE YOU SO AFRAID OF HIM?

194
00:11:25,667 --> 00:11:28,917
YOU SAID IT YOURSELF, HE'S THE
BADDEST MAN ON THE PLANET.

195
00:11:28,959 --> 00:11:31,583
I'M SUPPOSED TO DEFEAT HIM
AND SAVE THE WORLD.

196
00:11:31,625 --> 00:11:35,000
MMM, LIFE DOES FEEL THAT WAY
SOMETIMES, DOESN'T IT?

197
00:11:35,041 --> 00:11:38,875
LIKE WE'RE ALL TRYING TO
SAVE THE WORLD FROM EVIL?

198
00:11:38,917 --> 00:11:41,083
OK, BUT WHAT CAN I DO
TO FEEL BETTER?

199
00:11:41,125 --> 00:11:46,000
WANNA TRY SCREAMING
INTO THIS PILLOW?

200
00:11:46,041 --> 00:11:49,834
[MUFFLED SCREAM]

201
00:11:49,875 --> 00:11:51,208
[BAAS]

202
00:12:02,542 --> 00:12:04,250
Azula: HELLO, ZU-ZU.

203
00:12:04,291 --> 00:12:07,667
IF YOU'VE COME FOR A ROYAL
HAIR-COMBING, I'M AFRAID
YOU'LL HAVE TO WAIT.

204
00:12:07,709 --> 00:12:09,834
SO I GUESS THERE'S A BIG
WAR MEETING COMING UP, HUH?

205
00:12:09,875 --> 00:12:11,750
AND APPARENTLY I'M NOT
WELCOME THERE.

206
00:12:11,792 --> 00:12:14,667
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
OF COURSE YOU'RE WELCOME THERE.

207
00:12:14,709 --> 00:12:16,166
OH, YEAH?

208
00:12:16,208 --> 00:12:18,333
I GUESS THAT'S WHY NO ONE
BOTHERED TO TELL ME ABOUT IT.

209
00:12:18,375 --> 00:12:20,917
OH, ZUKO, DON'T BE SO DRAMATIC.

210
00:12:20,959 --> 00:12:22,709
I'M CERTAIN DAD WANTS YOU THERE.

211
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:24,709
YOU PROBABLY JUST
WEREN'T INVITED

212
00:12:24,750 --> 00:12:27,333
BECAUSE IT'S SO OBVIOUS THAT
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO BE THERE.

213
00:12:27,375 --> 00:12:29,083
WELL, WERE YOU INVITED?

214
00:12:29,125 --> 00:12:31,750
OF COURSE, I'M THE PRINCESS.

215
00:12:31,792 --> 00:12:33,542
AND I'M THE PRINCE.

216
00:12:33,583 --> 00:12:36,792
EXACTLY, SO STOP ACTING LIKE
A PARANOID CHILD.

217
00:12:36,834 --> 00:12:38,625
JUST GO TO THE MEETING.

218
00:12:38,667 --> 00:12:40,667
FORGET IT, I'M NOT GOING.

219
00:12:44,125 --> 00:12:48,500
Toph: ALL RIGHT, WHAT YOU NEED
IS A GOOD OLD-FASHIONED
BACK-POUNDING

220
00:12:48,542 --> 00:12:49,709
TO RELIEVE YOUR STRESS.

221
00:12:49,750 --> 00:12:51,709
POUND AWAY.

222
00:12:54,583 --> 00:12:56,750
AAH, OW...

223
00:12:56,792 --> 00:13:01,625
TOPH, I THINK
THIS IS BRUISING ME.

224
00:13:01,667 --> 00:13:04,792
[GRUNTING]

225
00:13:04,834 --> 00:13:08,166
SORRY, I FORGOT YOU HAVE
BABY SKIN.

226
00:13:08,208 --> 00:13:10,208
WELL, THERE'S ONE OTHER THING
WE CAN TRY.

227
00:13:13,250 --> 00:13:15,917
ACUPUNCTURE.

228
00:13:15,959 --> 00:13:17,875
[SCREAMS]

229
00:13:21,125 --> 00:13:24,000
ZUKO, IT'S JUST A DUMB MEETING.

230
00:13:24,041 --> 00:13:25,625
WHO CARES?

231
00:13:25,667 --> 00:13:27,083
I DON'T.

232
00:13:27,125 --> 00:13:29,083
WELL, GOOD, YOU SHOULDN'T.

233
00:13:29,125 --> 00:13:31,625
I MEAN, WHY WOULD YOU EVEN
WANT TO GO?

234
00:13:31,667 --> 00:13:34,917
JUST THINK ABOUT HOW THINGS WENT
AT THE LAST WAR MEETING
YOU WENT TO.

235
00:13:34,959 --> 00:13:37,208
[SIGHS] I KNOW.

236
00:13:37,250 --> 00:13:40,417
YOU KNOW WHAT WILL MAKE YOU
FEEL BETTER?

237
00:13:40,458 --> 00:13:43,041
ORDERING SOME SERVANTS AROUND.

238
00:13:43,083 --> 00:13:46,166
I MIGHT BE HUNGRY FOR
A WHOLE TRAY OF FRUIT TARTS.

239
00:13:46,208 --> 00:13:50,458
AND MAYBE A LITTLE PALANQUIN
RIDE AROUND TOWN, DOUBLE-TIME.

240
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:01,417
THANKS FOR EVERYTHING, GUYS.

241
00:14:01,458 --> 00:14:05,041
SO DO YOU FEEL LESS STRESSED,
READY FOR A GOOD NIGHT'S SLEEP?

242
00:14:05,083 --> 00:14:10,000
UH, I KIND OF THINK
I SORT OF MIGHT SLIGHTLY FEEL
A LITTLE BETTER.

243
00:14:10,041 --> 00:14:11,583
MAYBE.

244
00:14:11,625 --> 00:14:14,375
THEN OUR WORK HERE IS DONE.
[YAWNS]

245
00:14:14,417 --> 00:14:16,709
[KATARA AND TOPH YAWN]

246
00:14:22,291 --> 00:14:26,166
[THUNDER CRASHING]

247
00:14:26,208 --> 00:14:28,834
[CHATTERING]

248
00:14:36,375 --> 00:14:38,208
[DISTORTED VOICE]

249
00:14:45,333 --> 00:14:47,709
[SCREAMING]

250
00:14:51,625 --> 00:14:53,166
[GRUNTS]

251
00:14:57,208 --> 00:15:00,583
[OZAI CACKLING]

252
00:15:00,625 --> 00:15:02,417
[SCREAMS]

253
00:15:18,750 --> 00:15:20,250
SHH...

254
00:15:26,875 --> 00:15:28,875
[SCREAMS]

255
00:15:28,917 --> 00:15:31,250
[ROARS]

256
00:15:31,291 --> 00:15:33,041
WHAT HAPPENED, AANG?

257
00:15:33,083 --> 00:15:34,834
IT'S THE NIGHTMARES.

258
00:15:34,875 --> 00:15:37,208
THEY JUST GET WORSE AND WORSE.

259
00:15:37,250 --> 00:15:40,417
LOOKS LIKE IT'S TIME
FOR ANOTHER THERAPY SESSION.

260
00:15:40,458 --> 00:15:42,500
NO, THAT WON'T HELP.

261
00:15:42,542 --> 00:15:44,083
NOTHING HELPS.

262
00:15:44,125 --> 00:15:46,125
THERE'S ONLY ONE THING I CAN DO.

263
00:15:46,166 --> 00:15:48,792
I'M GONNA STAY AWAKE STRAIGHT
THROUGH TO THE INVASION.

264
00:15:57,709 --> 00:15:59,250
INVASION...

265
00:15:59,291 --> 00:16:01,875
ALL ABOARD FOR THE INVASION.

266
00:16:01,917 --> 00:16:04,000
YOU DON'T LOOK SO GOOD.

267
00:16:04,041 --> 00:16:06,959
YOU SURE YOU CAN'T JUST LIE DOWN
FOR A LITTLE NAP?

268
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,875
I TOLD YOU, I CAN'T
GO BACK TO SLEEP.

269
00:16:09,917 --> 00:16:12,583
AANG, STAYING UP ALL NIGHT
CAN'T BE GOOD FOR YOU.

270
00:16:12,625 --> 00:16:16,000
ACTUALLY, STAYING UP ALL NIGHT
HAS GIVEN ME SOME TIME TO THINK.

271
00:16:16,041 --> 00:16:18,458
AND I'VE REALIZED
SOME BIG THINGS, KATARA.

272
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:20,041
WHAT BIG THINGS?

273
00:16:20,083 --> 00:16:22,333
I SEE EVERYTHING
SO CLEARLY NOW.

274
00:16:22,375 --> 00:16:25,667
WHAT REALLY MATTERS,
WHY I'M REALLY DOING THIS.

275
00:16:25,709 --> 00:16:28,542
I'M DOING IT TO SAVE THE WORLD,
BUT MORE THAN THAT...

276
00:16:28,583 --> 00:16:30,667
I'M DOING IT FOR THE PEOPLE
I LOVE.

277
00:16:30,709 --> 00:16:33,083
I'M DOING IT FOR YOU, KATARA.

278
00:16:33,125 --> 00:16:35,125
AANG, WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

279
00:16:35,166 --> 00:16:38,083
I'M SAYING... I LOVE YOU.

280
00:16:46,959 --> 00:16:49,250
WHAT ARE WE DOING?

281
00:16:49,291 --> 00:16:53,125
WHAT OUR HEARTS HAVE BEEN
TELLING US TO DO
FOR A LONG, LONG TIME.

282
00:16:53,166 --> 00:16:55,792
BABY, YOU'RE MY FOREVER GIRL.

283
00:16:55,834 --> 00:16:57,959
Katara: AANG...

284
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,542
UH?

285
00:16:59,583 --> 00:17:02,917
I WAS JUST SAYING
YOU SHOULD TAKE A NAP.

286
00:17:02,959 --> 00:17:06,083
OH, I GUESS I KIND OF
DRIFTED OFF INTO A DAYDREAM.

287
00:17:06,125 --> 00:17:09,709
WHAT WAS YOUR DREAM ABOUT?

288
00:17:09,750 --> 00:17:11,709
UH, LIVING UNDERWATER.

289
00:17:11,750 --> 00:17:13,750
SOUNDS NEAT.

290
00:17:13,792 --> 00:17:16,166
[CHUCKLES]

291
00:17:16,208 --> 00:17:17,083
WHEW.

292
00:17:22,125 --> 00:17:24,375
PRINCE ZUKO, EVERYONE'S
WAITING FOR YOU.

293
00:17:24,417 --> 00:17:26,875
WHAT?

294
00:17:26,917 --> 00:17:29,291
THE HIGH ADMIRALS, HIGH
GENERALS, THE WAR MINISTERS, AND
THE PRINCESS HAVE ALL ARRIVED.

295
00:17:29,333 --> 00:17:31,166
YOU'RE THE ONLY PERSON MISSING.

296
00:17:31,208 --> 00:17:34,750
SO... MY DAD WANTS ME
AT THE MEETING?

297
00:17:34,792 --> 00:17:37,083
THE FIRE LORD SAID HE WOULD NOT
START UNTIL YOU ARRIVED, SIR.

298
00:17:45,333 --> 00:17:46,583
[EXHALES]

299
00:17:46,625 --> 00:17:49,417
PUT 'EM UP, FIRE LORD.

300
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:55,208
[YELLS]

301
00:17:55,250 --> 00:17:57,208
HEY, I'M TRYING TO BUILD APPA
SOME ARMOR HERE

302
00:17:57,250 --> 00:17:59,375
SO HE DOESN'T HAVE TO GO
INTO THE INVASION NAKED.

303
00:17:59,417 --> 00:18:00,959
HE'S YOUR BISON.

304
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:03,000
OZAI'S DEFENSE IS IMPECCABLE.

305
00:18:03,041 --> 00:18:05,917
I'LL HAVE TO TRY
A DIFFERENT APPROACH.

306
00:18:05,959 --> 00:18:07,792
[YELLS]

307
00:18:15,166 --> 00:18:18,041
YOU THINK YOU'RE UNTOUCHABLE,
DON'T YOU, MR. FIRE LORD?

308
00:18:18,083 --> 00:18:21,250
Voice: BOY, YOU ARE REALLY
STARTING TO LOSE IT, KID.

309
00:18:21,291 --> 00:18:26,667
MOMO, DID YOU HEAR SOMETHING?

310
00:18:26,709 --> 00:18:28,709
Voice: NO, BUT I SAID SOMETHING.

311
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:30,250
UH...

312
00:18:30,291 --> 00:18:34,000
YOU, MY FRIEND, ARE JUST A FEW
PLUMS SHORT OF A FRUIT PIE.

313
00:18:38,542 --> 00:18:42,750
[CHATTERING]

314
00:18:42,792 --> 00:18:44,542
THAT'S MORE LIKE IT.

315
00:18:44,583 --> 00:18:48,041
I'M SO TIRED THAT
FOR A SECOND THERE, I IMAGINED
YOU WERE TALKING TO ME.

316
00:18:48,083 --> 00:18:49,250
[CHATTERS]

317
00:18:49,291 --> 00:18:52,000
OH, MOMO, LET ME EXPLAIN.

318
00:18:52,041 --> 00:18:55,250
[CHATTERING]

319
00:18:55,291 --> 00:18:58,166
[MOMO CHATTERING]

320
00:18:58,208 --> 00:19:02,083
[LAUGHING, CHATTERING]

321
00:19:02,125 --> 00:19:04,000
Katara: AANG?

322
00:19:04,041 --> 00:19:06,834
WE'RE ALL STARTING TO GET
A LITTLE WORRIED ABOUT YOU.

323
00:19:06,875 --> 00:19:09,000
YOU'VE BEEN AWAKE TOO LONG.

324
00:19:09,041 --> 00:19:11,959
AND YOU'RE ACTING
DOWNRIGHT WEIRD.

325
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:14,792
YOU'VE GOT TO TAKE CARE
OF YOURSELF.

326
00:19:14,834 --> 00:19:17,291
YOU CAN'T GO ON LIKE THIS.

327
00:19:17,333 --> 00:19:21,125
[GROANS] LOOK, I APPRECIATE
WHAT YOU GUYS ARE SAYING

328
00:19:21,166 --> 00:19:23,208
BUT THE STRESS
AND THE NIGHTMARES...

329
00:19:23,250 --> 00:19:25,166
THEY WERE JUST TOO MUCH.

330
00:19:25,208 --> 00:19:27,917
STAYING AWAKE IS THE BEST WAY
FOR ME TO DEAL WITH IT.

331
00:19:27,959 --> 00:19:29,959
YEAH, LEAVE THE KID ALONE.

332
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:32,125
HEY, WHO ASKED YOU?

333
00:19:32,166 --> 00:19:34,375
Aang: GUYS, COME ON.

334
00:19:34,417 --> 00:19:37,083
NO, I AM SICK OF THIS GUY

335
00:19:37,125 --> 00:19:40,208
ALWAYS MOUTHING OFF
AND TELLING ME WHAT TO DO.

336
00:19:40,250 --> 00:19:41,083
OH, YOU DON'T LIKE IT?

337
00:19:41,125 --> 00:19:42,375
WELL, LET'S GO RIGHT NOW.

338
00:19:42,417 --> 00:19:45,041
SOKKA, WHAT SHOULD WE DO?

339
00:19:45,083 --> 00:19:46,083
ABOUT WHAT?

340
00:19:46,125 --> 00:19:48,834
ABOUT THAT.

341
00:19:56,834 --> 00:19:59,875
[ROARING]

342
00:19:59,917 --> 00:20:01,917
[SCREECHING]

343
00:20:01,959 --> 00:20:03,166
[SWORDS CLANG]

344
00:20:07,875 --> 00:20:10,250
APPA, APPA, APPA.

345
00:20:10,291 --> 00:20:12,458
MOMO, MOMO, MOMO.

346
00:20:22,041 --> 00:20:25,875
COME ON, GUYS, WE'RE ALL
ON THE SAME SIDE.

347
00:20:25,917 --> 00:20:30,041
♪ CHAKRAS, CHAKRAS,
EVERYBODY LOVES CHAKRAS ♪

348
00:20:30,083 --> 00:20:32,959
♪ CHAKRAS, CHAKRAS ♪

349
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:35,166
♪ CHAKRA SANDWICH
TASTES GOOD, YUM... ♪

350
00:20:40,750 --> 00:20:43,125
YAY, YAY, YAY, YAY, YAY!

351
00:20:45,834 --> 00:20:48,166
[WHIMPERS]

352
00:20:53,166 --> 00:20:54,792
[CHEERING]

353
00:21:03,291 --> 00:21:05,875
I JUST NEED TO JUMP IN
A COLD WATERFALL.

354
00:21:05,917 --> 00:21:08,709
[SCREAMING]

355
00:21:15,417 --> 00:21:17,959
SO HOW DID IT GO?

356
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:21,166
WHEN I GOT TO THE MEETING,
EVERYONE WELCOMED ME.

357
00:21:21,208 --> 00:21:23,208
MY FATHER HAD SAVED ME A SEAT.

358
00:21:23,250 --> 00:21:25,083
HE WANTED ME NEXT TO HIM.

359
00:21:25,125 --> 00:21:27,583
I WAS LITERALLY
AT HIS RIGHT HAND.

360
00:21:27,625 --> 00:21:29,417
ZUKO, THAT'S WONDERFUL.

361
00:21:29,458 --> 00:21:32,166
YOU MUST BE HAPPY.

362
00:21:37,125 --> 00:21:40,917
DURING THE MEETING,
I WAS THE PERFECT PRINCE.

363
00:21:40,959 --> 00:21:43,834
THE SON MY FATHER WANTED.

364
00:21:43,875 --> 00:21:46,083
BUT I WASN'T ME.

365
00:22:02,709 --> 00:22:05,166
OH, LOOK, ANOTHER HALLUCINATION.

366
00:22:05,208 --> 00:22:07,750
AN IMAGINARY BED
MADE OUT OF CLOUDS.

367
00:22:07,792 --> 00:22:09,208
Toph: HEY, IT'S REAL.

368
00:22:09,250 --> 00:22:11,125
WE SPENT HOURS WORKING ON IT.

369
00:22:11,166 --> 00:22:12,625
WE MADE IT FOR YOU.

370
00:22:12,667 --> 00:22:14,583
A GOOD NIGHT'S SLEEP WILL
PROBABLY TAKE THE CRAZY AWAY.

371
00:22:14,625 --> 00:22:16,250
WE HOPE.

372
00:22:16,291 --> 00:22:19,291
LOOK, YOU GUYS KEEP TELLING ME
I NEED TO SLEEP, BUT I CAN'T.

373
00:22:19,333 --> 00:22:21,458
THE INVASION'S TOMORROW.

374
00:22:21,500 --> 00:22:22,875
AANG...

375
00:22:22,917 --> 00:22:25,041
NO, KATARA, THERE'S STILL
SO MUCH I HAVEN'T LEARNED.

376
00:22:25,083 --> 00:22:28,291
I DON'T NEED SLEEP,
WHAT I NEED IS PRACTICE.

377
00:22:28,333 --> 00:22:30,750
QUICK, HIT ME.

378
00:22:30,792 --> 00:22:32,166
I'M NOT GOING TO HIT YOU.

379
00:22:32,208 --> 00:22:33,917
YOU WANT ME TO DO IT?

380
00:22:33,959 --> 00:22:35,667
LISTEN TO ME.

381
00:22:35,709 --> 00:22:38,083
YOU'VE BEEN TRAINING FOR THIS
SINCE THE DAY WE MET.

382
00:22:38,125 --> 00:22:40,000
I'VE SEEN YOUR PROGRESS.

383
00:22:40,041 --> 00:22:43,125
YOU'RE SMART, BRAVE,
AND STRONG ENOUGH.

384
00:22:43,166 --> 00:22:44,750
YOU REALLY THINK SO?

385
00:22:44,792 --> 00:22:45,750
WE ALL DO.

386
00:22:45,792 --> 00:22:48,709
YOU CAN DO THIS,
YOU'RE READY.

387
00:22:48,750 --> 00:22:50,667
YOU'RE THE MAN, TWINKLE TOES.

388
00:22:50,709 --> 00:22:54,625
THANKS, GUYS.

389
00:22:54,667 --> 00:22:56,375
[YAWNS]

390
00:23:00,208 --> 00:23:02,208
[YAWNS]

391
00:23:02,250 --> 00:23:04,083
YOU KNOW WHAT?

392
00:23:04,125 --> 00:23:06,542
I THINK I AM READY.

393
00:23:14,959 --> 00:23:17,375
YOUR DAYS OF TYRANNY
ARE OVER, FIRE LORD.

394
00:23:17,417 --> 00:23:20,333
REALLY, YOU'RE GOING TO
TAKE ME OUT?

395
00:23:20,375 --> 00:23:23,875
YOU'RE NOT EVEN WEARING PANTS.

396
00:23:23,917 --> 00:23:27,083
NO, FIRE LORD OZAI,
<i>YOU'RE</i> NOT WEARING PANTS.

397
00:23:27,125 --> 00:23:30,083
[GASPS, SCREAMS]

398
00:23:30,125 --> 00:23:31,750
NO!

399
00:23:31,792 --> 00:23:34,792
MY ROYAL PARTS ARE SHOWING.

400
00:23:34,834 --> 00:23:37,000
[OZAI SCREAMS]

401
00:23:50,375 --> 00:23:53,875
♪
